\begin_layout Section
Nash Equilibrium
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
So far we considered reasonable ways of playing a game, dominated and dominating
 strategies and their elimination.
 Nash equilibrium is an 
\series bold
equilibrium
\series default
 (a profile of strategies that has a property, that everyone's strategy
 is a best-response strategy to everyone else's stratgy - i.e there is no
 reason for deviation).
 It has been established as a best prediction of how games would be played
 (which is, in fact, not always right).
\end_layout

